%section
  .container
    .col-md-12.align-center
      .section-heading
        %br/
        %br/
        %br/
        %h1 Quickbox Overview
        %p.align-center
          By breaking free of traditional self storage or PODs (TM) we're able to find tons of ways to save you money, time and hassle while delivering quality service. We've simply found a way to go above and beyond for our customers. No more driving that big moving truck, or hauling all your stuff to the sketchy part of town to your storage locker. You won't ever have to carry your sofa sleeper down the stairs, rent a truck or be stuck traveling to get the one thing you want back. 
        %p.align-center
           
        %br/
        %br/
