        %p.width-80-no-mgn We transport all of your stuff to our secure storage facility, where its safe and insured.
      .col-md-4.align-center
        %h3.black.lowercase We Deliver
        %img.width-80-no-mgn{:src => "https://s3.amazonaws.com/storage_rails_app_dev/images/homepage_bg_1.png", :alt => ""}/
